<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Arsinoite</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>χαῖρε, κύριέ μου Ἑρμᾶ. 

    <lb n="2"/>καλῶς <choice><corr>ποιήσεις</corr><sic>ποιησις</sic></choice> μὴ ἀμελή-

    <lb n="3"/>σας ἀνελθεῖν ἔχων τὴν 

    <lb n="4"/>πρόσοδον καὶ τὰ τοῦ μέ-

    <lb n="5"/>τρου. ἀλλὰ καὶ δὸς τὰ ναῦ-

    <lb n="6"/>λα τῷ μέλλοντι αὐτὰ 

    <lb n="7"/><choice><corr>μεταφέρειν</corr><sic>μεταφεριν</sic></choice> ἐπὶ τὴν Φι-

    <lb n="8"/>λαγρίδα, ἀλλ᾽ ἵνα καὶ κω-

    <lb n="9"/>μάρχας ἀναδῶται καὶ 

    <lb n="10"/>περὶ <choice><corr>ὧν</corr><sic>των</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἀνηλώκατε</corr><sic>αναλωκαται</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>μάθηται πῶς <choice><corr>μέλλει</corr><sic>μελλι</sic></choice> ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="12"/>παραδέχεσθαι. ἤδη γὰρ κα-

    <lb n="13"/>τέλαβεν ὁ ἕτερος μηνιαῖος. 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὐχόμεθα. </ab></div><div n="meta.11172" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.11172" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low" notBefore="0249" notAfter="0268">ca. 249 - 268</date></p></div><div n="meta.11172" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört wahrscheinlich zum Heroninos - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.11172" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.11172" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Flor.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">345</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">11172</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0111</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">345</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0111;3;345" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.11172" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">74</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.11172" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.11172" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><geogName type="nome" cert="high" full="yes">Arsinoites</geogName>, <geogName type="ancientRegion" key="Aegyptus" cert=